/protocols.html | title = History of the Protocols of the Learned Elders of Zion | publisher = [[Freemasonry]] | place = BCY, [[Canada|CA]]}}. * {{Citation | contribution-url = http://www.britannica.com/EBchecked/topic/480269/Protocols-of-the-Learned-Elders-of-Zion | contribution = Protocols of the Learned Elders of Zion | title = Encyclopaedia [[Britannica]]}}.
